      Parameters:
      teamA - The first team.
      teamB - The second team.
      match - The match.
      totalTime - The total time of the match.
      penaltyEnd - Whether the match ended in a penalty shootout.
      tAgoals - The goals scored by team A.
      tBgoals - The goals scored by team B.
      tAYellowCards - The yellow cards received by team A.
      tBYellowCards - The yellow cards received by team B.
      tARedCards - The red cards received by team A.
      tBRedCards - The red cards received by team B.
      Throws:
      LogInMatchException - If either team has no players.
